headline: Holiday Magic Continues at Best Buy, Black Friday Sale Begins Nov. 21
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 18, 2024--It’s time to kick the holiday shopping into high gear. Best Buy’s Black Friday Sale1 starts this Thursday, Nov. 21—more than a week before Black Friday—and it’s packed with the best deals and doorbusters on all the hottest tech before the turkey even hits the table.
